  m_text: '1. Check each person you encounter for symptoms using the tools available


    2.
    Fill out ALL findings regardless of if you believe they are infected


    3.
    Decide whether they are infected and submit the checklist


    4. Repeat this
    until the days end


    You may view symptoms to look for in your notes during
    this time, or on the home page of this application


    Please remember your
    performance is monitored'
